The paper presents a deep learning variant of thresholded lexicographic Q-learning for the task of urban driving, which involves multiple aspects such as avoiding collision, obeying traffic rules, and ensuring passenger comfort. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Robotics (cs.RO), Computer Vision (cs.CV), and Systems and Control (cs.SY).
